Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗户...要是一直开着的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你再怎么傻也是会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(日本有傻瓜不会感冒的说法)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会冷的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.05,0:01:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的还很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为才刚进二月而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便利店里有很多杂志上登着巧克力的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为吃了巧克力就会暖和起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.85,0:01:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为情人节就快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人节?

