Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:03:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}[...踏上旅途的人.]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2月14日是情人节呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要在艾草保育园办情人节会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要在保育园办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保育园不办的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概有的保育园会办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在日本也就是送巧克力的日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 书里也是这么写的 所以我们也办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生给男生送吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是女生送巧克力给喜欢的男生的日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?情人节是这么回事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 最近反过来的好像也有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你还真是什么都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给喜欢的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办办看吧 情人节会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师 最近又好像总在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常难受 却又努力不让别人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让清花老师在情人节那天能精神一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在园里已经没有余钱来办这种活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chiroru会分给我们一些材料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上去店里商量了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做巧克力需要的材料用兼职来换就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 去蛋糕店chiroru帮忙做事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换来保育园的大家做巧克力需要的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这样跟人家交涉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 有什么地方行不通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼职安排太满 给chiroru帮忙恐怕很难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半夜里都安排了工地的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙的事情就我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始每天保育园放学以后去帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到情人节那天为止就行了 店长这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了情人节 小鸠会加油的!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!加油加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠要在园里办情人节会?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个温柔的孩子呢 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会继续努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想这样拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今天已经到关店的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?已经这么晚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个那个 有什么其他的能帮忙的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离情人节还有两天 你已经帮了不少忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 能把外面的看板收进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又以这种奇怪的方式掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回又不是海上之类的 有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次可差一点就要死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:07:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是女孩子!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有人的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界白馒头一样的东西会不会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...这个人叫做黑钢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶...诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 我叫法伊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上这位是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫柯那 说话也不要紧的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看她一点都不吃惊的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会说话的玩偶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想摸鱼到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫五百祗先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫莫柯那 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那游乐园的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们正在旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四人一起?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人和一莫柯那一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一莫柯那?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫柯那的数量单位哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢 哪有那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑钢和五百祗先生的声音真的很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:09:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界的黑钢 蓝蓝的小小的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我住嘴 白馒头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你们是旅行到此?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在书里读到过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行要在很多地方过夜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经决定在哪里过夜了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有什么地方能让我们留宿的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有这个世界的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在身上带的大概不能用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很发愁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不过没有女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以露宿也没问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫柯那就是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里能够区分性别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜色?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱程度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 如果发愁的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来我家住一晚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 有房间的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过被褥只有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家叠在一块的睡话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是又有块头比较大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上边的被子和下边的褥子分开来盖的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一套被褥就是说 一个人住?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还有五百祗先生一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话越发不妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭敬不如从命嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我说你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果发生什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有五百祗先生保护的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 向小鸠家 go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,go go的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有什么打算的吧 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这么酷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么想 也许还真的什么都没想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天保育园休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早一定要去chiroru的说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经叫过你许多次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠睡的很香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不管房间里有什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一点都不变呢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我这就要出门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要在意 只管呆在房间里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠是要去蛋糕店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 去帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了获得情人节用来做巧克力的材料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 作为留我们住的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕店啊 这个嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君 你陪她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做料理很厉害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑作为蛋糕店员的话有点...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不想去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑和我去其他地方打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筹集资金
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫柯那呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和五百祗先生在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为觉得和你很亲近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲密的两个人的连携play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲密个屁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生情不自禁地嫉妒莫柯那的可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美 那个男孩子是...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像是小鸠的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装布偶的样子 莫柯那很擅长的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:13:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说话啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼先生真的非常手巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟能生巧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我练习了多少次都没法包好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要总想一次塞进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你呐 不要唱歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼先生你们 一直都在旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 并不是有目的地的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是次把不断旅行作为目的的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说还没有决定去哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要决定很难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在同一个地方呆多久都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人一直等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直等着不知下次何时会回来的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...有一个想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为去到那个地方有什么意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说去到那里以后有你想见到的人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见的...人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的...想见的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了很多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是坐在那里而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以是作为看板莫柯那的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕店那边如何了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼先生很手巧 店长也一直夸奖他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也说了这衣服很少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 衣服啊 我们也很辛苦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有人问这是COSPLAY吗什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为你说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这在这个世界是不是算是COSPLAY呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才弄得解释不清的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟只有一天 没有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是 可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你肯收下我们会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是给你留我们住的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 我会为艾草保育园使用它的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当这个耳饰亮起来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要前往下一个世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我们住下来真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是两天一夜 但是很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没帮到各位什么忙实在是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 小鸠她啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 好像十分不安定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊 好美的光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是莫柯那最喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在其他世界只能祝福她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也包含我们的份在内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你照顾好她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你说我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去到就好了 你想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从其他世界来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为世界并不只有这个人间界而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天界 地界 异界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了这些可能还有其他许多不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望小狼先生他们下一个去到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是等待他们的人所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(情人节会 加油)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 那个借我用下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠真的很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛...是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠你那个的形状真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:20:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是想做成星星的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是海星吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?像海星先生吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了巧克力她还给了我钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连装巧克力的包装盒还有卡片都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 没有勉强自己就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 义男君要把巧克力送给谁呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈 还有妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要送给妈妈...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有送一份给小鸠也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要把最好的巧克力送给最喜欢的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠要把最好的送给谁呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠那家伙 有留我那份的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.73,0:22:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠她...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没多少时间了...

Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:11.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}なくしたものと あつめたものの狭間に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:11.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}所失与所得的缝隙中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:20.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}あなたの笑顔　落ちていたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:20.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}遗落着你的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:26.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}届きそうで　届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:26.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}仿佛伸手可及却又遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:32.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}飛んでゆけるわけじゃないし
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:32.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}飞又飞不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:38.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}笑わせてあげたいだけなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:38.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我只是想让你有更多笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.53,0:23:43.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}役立たずのこの翼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.53,0:23:43.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}这没用的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:49.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}何のためにあるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:49.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}到底为什么存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:55.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}あなたの傍で笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:55.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我会在你身边微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:24:00.67,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}私に出来ること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:24:00.67,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}这是我能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.16,0:24:07.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}暖めるだけでもいいのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.16,0:24:07.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}哪怕给你一丝为暖也好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:12.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}せめて包みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:12.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}至少想包容着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.59,0:24:19.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}気付くの　そのための翼と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.59,0:24:19.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}终于发觉 双翼是为此存在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.65,0:24:27.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}今こそわたし　笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.65,0:24:27.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}所以我现在 在微笑

Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.17,0:24:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[...春天的脚步声.]
